org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.storage
Interface IAeProcessSnapshot

All Known Implementing Classes:
AeProcessSnapshot
public interface IAeProcessSnapshot

Defines the interface for process snapshots that contain all variables and correlation sets that are live for normal or compensation processing.
